{"tid":1262411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青島應該一早要抵制!!!","createTime":"2019-06-27T16:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:48:28.000Z","uid":13095,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26ccf3c949517d4201292eb48a6fd0df8c3f791c","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"<ins>歷史篇</ins><br />\n1903年，由來自德國的商人聯合投資40萬德國馬克在青島成立了日耳曼啤酒公司青島股份公司，採用德國的釀造技術以及原料，號稱使用嶗山（位於青島東部）礦泉水釀造，在中國生產德國風味的啤酒，主要供應一些在中國的德國人和另外一些西方人。<br />\n<br />\n1914年，第一次世界大戰爆發以後，日本侵占青島。1916年，日本人侵占了德國商人的股份，買下英國商人的股份，將公司更名為「大日本麥酒株式會社青島工場」。生產品牌除原青島啤酒外，也生產日本大麥酒旗下品牌朝日啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n青島啤酒的燈籠<br />\n1945年隨著日本的戰敗，中華民國政府成立行政院收復區全國性事業接收委員會，沒收日本在中國之資產，於是工廠由青島市政府當局派員接管，更名為「青島啤酒公司」，隸屬於行政院山東青島區產業處理局。1947年6月14日，由中國國民黨黨營企業「齊魯企業股份有限公司」購買，成為「齊魯企業青島啤酒廠」。1949年，中華人民共和國的成立，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">青島啤酒被中國共產黨沒收，更名為「國營青島啤酒廠」。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史睇到呢到夠，因為之後青島就係支那嘅天下。<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9D%92%E5%B2%9B%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B2%259B%25E5%2595%25A4%25E9%2585%2592&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=f50f325e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%9D%92%E5%B2%9B%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>股東篇</ins><br />\n前十股東(排名不分先後)<br />\n<strong>1 青島啤酒集團有限公司 </strong><br />\n2 香港中央結算(代理人)有限公司 <br />\n<strong>3 全國社保基金四一八組合</strong><br />\n<strong>4 中國證券金融股份有限公司</strong><br />\n<strong>5 中國人民人壽保險股份有限公司-分紅-個險分紅</strong><br />\n<strong>6 中國建銀投資有限責任公司 </strong><br />\n7 香港中央結算有限公司<br />\n<strong>8 中央匯金資產管理有限責任公司</strong><br />\n9 香港金融管理局-自有資金<br />\n<strong>10 中國工商銀行股份有限公司-南方消費活力靈活配置混合型發起式證券投資基金</strong><br />\n<br />\n支那Source:<br />\n<a href=\"http://money.finance.sina.com.cn/corp/go.php/vCI_StockHolder/stockid/600600/displaytype/30.phtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmoney.finance.sina.com.cn%2Fcorp%2Fgo.php%2FvCI_StockHolder%2Fstockid%2F600600%2Fdisplaytype%2F30.phtml&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=8c61def2\" target=\"_blank\">http://money.finance.sina.com.cn/corp/go.php/vCI_StockHolder/stockid/600600/displaytype/30.phtml</a><br />\n邪惡青島故意頂走公開信，原來背後有更大勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n健康篇<br />\n15款啤酒入面致癌含量最高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在15款啤酒中，草甘膦含量最高是「青島」樣本，有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">49.7ppb</span>（parts per million）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其次為「Coors Light」樣本有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">31.1ppb</span>，而受港人熱愛的品牌如「喜力」及「Stella Artois」啤酒，則分別含有<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">20.9ppb</span>及<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">18.7ppb</span>。<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2280202/15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2280202%2F15&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPJIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=51d82d30\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2280202/15</a><br />\n<br />\n大家為咗自己健康，唔好再飲致癌嘅青島啤酒，戒青島啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c71d268fa1cfd9c929c2073245a49a380a5494a","tid":1262411,"uid":132942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"961315b824c6d1a1210a4577752ccc2e98704e47","tid":1262411,"uid":132942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a5b261f813a4a43435e22f8698f4fb00c14b0c","tid":1262411,"uid":261071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"4fa3e4ebbbd2c515798ddd4fef24b30f216919f1","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:39:53.000Z","msg":"搶走頭版，宣傳致癌啤酒，危害天下百姓，不能饒恕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781e85095209b8d53fc32a26eedc34d27c8f6fdc","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e934ca4183a28126e9863f069cf5ca57f33c27a2","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:41:45.000Z","msg":"抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42cb96cac9da831147d2531befea1ce848e809b","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283d7254bed409310f8363d703cdd3bdb3bab953","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa53624f0c12241976d3b84316fcbbc2eddfe9f","tid":1262411,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7369954f28465b33f10f1921d956993c50d30f9","tid":1262411,"uid":249965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:48:28.000Z","msg":"其實我係幾鍾意飲青島<br />\n不過以後唔撚飲<br />\n再飲就切J<br />\n基本上大陸嘢乜撚都唔應該掂"}]}